      "Title": "TextFx.Mask",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/TextFx.Mask.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A simple fractional mask that defines a range within the [0-1] space.</p>\n<p>\nUsed to determine which characters should be affected by a group based on their\nposition within the text. Values are fractional [0-1] and does not depend on the actual width.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/TextFx.ModificationContext.yml",
