      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "TextFx.ModificationContext",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/TextFx.ModificationContext.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Context used internally to compute and pass modified character information\nacross all groups and their modifiers sequentially.\nEach modifier applies its properties to this context, which accumulates\nthe final transformation, color, and opacity for each character.</p>\n"
    },
