      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "TextFx.PlateauCurve",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/TextFx.PlateauCurve.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A special type of curve that starts rising from 0 to 1 following a profile (Rising profile),\nis 1 for a certain range, and then falls back to 0 following another profile (Falling profile).</p>\n<p>\nThe values used are fractional i.e, 0 is considered the starting point and 1, the ending point no matter\nthe actual width of the range it is applied to.\n</p>\n"
    },
